<h1>Welcome to the project template.</h1>
<p>The project template is an extention of the <a href="https://github.com/jamierumbelow/codeigniter-base-controller">CodeIgniter Base Controller</a>, which is an extention of the <a href="http://ellislab.com/codeigniter/user-guide/">CodeIgniter PHP Framework</a>.</p>
<p>A copy of the MySQL database is located in the /dev directory.</p>
<p>Please make use of the additional models, helpers, and libraries that we include in the project template.</p>
<p>If you find yourself using models, layouts, views, libraries, etc. in more than one project, please add them to the project template to speed up future development.</p>
